      <title>卢拉希望在不激怒唐纳德·特朗普的情况下拉拢习近平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-13/lula-quiere-cortejar-a-xi-jinping-sin-enfadar-a-donald-trump-m3gfd34x</link>
